district court bench in new york city said judges have little 
choice but to trust police when they say they have an informant 
assuming that they were trying to trick me how would i know 
it weinstein said the informant isnt subject to cross 
examination i dont even see the informant i have to rely on the 
us attorney and the law enforcement agencies if they wanted to 
deceive me it would be easy to do so 
