the sun will be partly obscured tuesday morning 
in an eclipse visible in the western portions of the united states 
and canada the us naval observatory reports 
the sun will be as much as 80 percent hidden for residents of 
western alaska and hawaii while lesser amounts will be obscured in 
other areas 
