494000 children from causes directly attributable to malnutrition 
associated with the war 
mozambique is one of the worlds poorest countries two of every 
10 babies born here die before their first birthday according to 
the unicef report as many as 375 children out of 1000 die before 
the age of five among the highest rates in the world the report 
said 
