city he read off a list of the 20 most dangerous assembly district 
in the state including abramsons 
all were in the city and all but one were represented by 
legislators who had voted against the death penalty bill previously 
under the bill the most coldblooded murderers paid hitmen 
killers of police officers those murdering witnesses and the like 
would be subject to the death penalty once a murder verdict was 
delivered a second jury would be asked to decide whether the death 
penalty should be imposed 
