carpet 
one day people are all lined up along the carpet their legs 
are like fence posts the ducks havent got anyplace else to go 
except to the fountain and back to the elevator 
they might be a little confused on the first day after that 
they do just what i want them to do 
they get to know my voice they know im the one who feeds 
them they also know im the one with the stick 
