three months later he unveiled a plan to turn the airline around 
with a program that included marketing expansions and cutting labor 
costs overall by 490 million or about 30 percent he has promised 
eastern which has shrunk steadily under texas air will be rebuilt 
to grow if its labor costs can be cut 
